My name is Jay Moss, and I'm looking for anyone that served<br>
with me at Ban Me Thuot from Feb 68 thru Jan 69. I was in the radio section of Det. 9, 619th Tac Con Sq, out of saigon. We were a radio and radar site in the middle of<br>
an Army helicopter oufit. I can't remember the chopper<br>
outfit number, but I remember some of us flew with them every chance we got. I know where two of my buddies are,<br>
but one still can't or wont talk about Nam and the other<br>
one doesn't know where anyone is either. Any help will<br>
be greatly appreciated.
